{"tid":2208965,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜據報周末慎重考慮是否收緊英格蘭地區抗疫措施","createTime":"2020-09-19T09:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T10:27:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ac72c30e6df9521559997d67a12077c90386d0c8","tid":2208965,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550540-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550540-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=124e89d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550540-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=90e2bd56\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550540-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒報道，首相約翰遜在今個周末，會慎重考慮是否收緊英格蘭地區的抗疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n新型肺炎疫情近期在英國反彈，星期五新增超過4300宗個案，是5月8日以來首次單日宗數突破4000。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，政府研究禁止舉行涉及多個家庭的聚會，並減少酒吧及餐廳的營業時間。約翰遜有權直接對英格蘭地區，頒布抗疫限制措施；蘇格蘭、威爾士及北愛爾蘭地區，可因應情況自行頒布。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，倫敦市長簡世德說，抗疫措施似乎有增加的需要；而在全國最少1350萬人，即是約五分之一人口，正受各地政府不同程度的限制措施影響。"},{"pid":"8106e13532977e8c7b79fe2e6e988ac546b64deb","tid":2208965,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"tui"}]}